rails_assviz allows you to quickly see how your Rails models interrelate with their associations.
Requires that you have Graphviz (http://www.graphviz.org) installed.
Works with Rails 2.3.11 and ruby-graphviz 1.0.0

Example usage:
ruby ./rails_assviz.rb --in=~/projects/myrailsapp/ --out=~/Desktop/assviz --format=png,pdf --program=dot
